About the course
Julington Creek Golf Club
Julington Creek Golf Club
Better than ever!
Julington Creek, formerly known as Champions Club, offers 18 holes of championship golf full of surprises and unique challenges.
The golf course was renovated in the summer of 2022. The bunkers were rebuilt with new drainage and sand, tee boxes were laser leveled and sodded, and the greens were reconstructed and then sprigged with TifEagle bermuda grass.

Rental Clubs
TaylorMade rental sets are available for $40 for 18 holes and $25 for 9 holes.  Club rentals require a drivers license and credit card to be saved on file. Call ahead to confirm availability.
Driving Range
Open to the public. $15 for a Large basket of balls and $10 for Small.
Current range tee schedule:
Hit from mat Monday – Thursday. From the grass Friday – Sunday

Practice Facility
Julington Creek Golf Club features a full-size driving range to suit your practice needs. Also, a large chipping green & putting green are available free of cost. Making this a golfers paradise.
Come spend some time refining your game or spend a few minutes prior to your tee time to loosen up!
